   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Hathyr 12. Sarapion, son of Chairemon, has brought, for the village of Karanis, for the tenth indiction, one-hundred and twenty litrai of chaff, 120. And, through Isiak, son of Ision, one-hundred and twenty litrai, 120. (2nd hand?) I, Souchidas, have signed.</ab>
